  1292Ôćĺ## FAQ
  1294Ôćĺ#### How do I use this in Node.js?
  1296ÔćĺNode.js 18 and later supports `fetch` natively, so you can just use this package directly.
  1297Ôćĺ
  1339Ôćĺ## Browser support
  1341ÔćĺThe latest version of Chrome, Firefox, and Safari.
  1342Ôćĺ
  1343Ôćĺ## Node.js support
  1345ÔćĺNode.js 18 and later.
  1346Ôćĺ
  1347Ôćĺ## Related
  1349Ôćĺ- [fetch-extras](https://github.com/sindresorhus/fetch-extras) - Useful utilities for working with Fetch
  1350Ôćĺ- [ky-hooks-change-case](https://github.com/alice-health/ky-hooks-change-case) - Ky hooks to modify cases on requests and responses of objects
  1351Ôćĺ
